title: How I Broke Bad Habits & Raised My Vibration
description:
This week Camo talks about the life changes and personal growth they've gone through this year from learning to set boundaries to investing their time and energy into themselves instead of others. Camo is raising their vibrational frequency and wants to help you do it too!
For 50% off your first Care/of order, go to TakeCareOf.com and enter code unfazed50.
Watch "Unfazed and Unbothered" on YouTube
If you like the show, telling a friend about it would be helpful! You can text, email, Tweet, or send this link to a friend: https://bit.ly/UnfazedandUnbotheredPodcast
